data.body:
Looking through the different mods, wiki and WarheadInfo I've seen no way to tell a warhead with a large spread not to damage friendly (allied or own) units/buildings in its spread range.

I would assume that IsValidAgainst (with ValidTargets and InvalidTargets) within WarheadInfo would be the place to add this into.

Ex: InvalidTarget = { "Friend", "Neutral" } or ValidTarget = { "Foe" }
